I think that Tom and Sue Falafel have done an outstanding job putting together this pickleball program.

89
00:09:56,403 --> 00:10:01,787
And I also think Kevin Bailey has been fantastic

90
00:10:02,515 --> 00:10:08,578
I've tried to help pick a ball to a lot of towns and Kevin has been one of the most receptive people.

