131
00:13:53,277 --> 00:13:54,918
So you have to do the diversity.

132
00:13:55,919 --> 00:14:06,087
But when you don't have to do that, it makes it a lot easier to manage if you don't have so many different kinds of funding brought to the table.

133
00:14:07,048 --> 00:14:09,630
