193
00:19:30,614 --> 00:19:37,238
And we've talked about this before is is the nibbling away process that seems to be going on with these parks.

194
00:19:38,459 --> 00:19:42,261
And you know, there has to be some some sort of balance here, you know,

195
00:19:43,076 --> 00:19:50,420
