00:54:50,818 --> 00:54:54,501
But they actually cause a lot of supervision hazards.

546
00:54:54,641 --> 00:54:55,842
They don't provide any shade.

547
00:54:56,042 --> 00:54:59,684
And nobody understands it out there about the river anymore.

548
00:54:59,864 --> 00:55:03,187
So we're moving on from that design choice.

