00:59:19,228 --> 00:59:22,953
So, our community outreach we have done significant on site events.

598
00:59:23,694 --> 00:59:29,222
We've surveyed all elementary families, because we'll be looking to do future work.

599
00:59:30,893 --> 00:59:39,918
