797
01:20:59,309 --> 01:21:11,118
The rest of it is actually concrete or asphalt, which allows it to be more durable and not need as many repairs as well as being able to be there for inclement weather.

798
01:21:11,138 --> 01:21:15,081
So if you see the difference between that and the

799
01:21:18,117 --> 01:21:19,058
the amount of poured in place.

