811
01:22:27,431 --> 01:22:41,315
There's no considerations of how does a student with autism, how does a student with a gross motor skill disability, how do students with any variety of disabilities, how does flow and supervision work?

812
01:22:42,515 --> 01:22:48,116
You have to invest in design studies to make sure that this work is done right.

813
01:22:48,876 --> 01:22:51,337
